One of the big reasons I left my first wife...  She had a teaching degree, could work anywhere she wanted to.  But she flat out decided why work, if she could sit at home and get money from the government for being poor.  She threw all kinds of shit fits when I started climbing the corporate ladder, and accepted jobs that got her kicked off her government programs.  /boggle<br>
<br>
